{"id":"806819458811297792","type":"text","timestamp":1769442995,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/806819458811297792","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/sapphic-dice/805469331730399232\">sapphic-dice</a>:</p><blockquote><p>I never know if someone is flirting with me, likewise I never know if I’m flirting either. </p><p>The answer to both usually ends up being yes, but I’m also an idiot so hah.</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"sapphic-dice"},"post":{"id":"805469331730399232"}}],"baseline_notes":66,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}